    "Off by default. Only enable if your collective agreement allows transferring unused annual leave; consult HR / legal. When on, unused annual days for the year may be added to the next year\u2019s carryover opening, subject to the maximum carryover cap above." : "Fra som standard. Aktiver kun, hvis din overenskomst tillader overf\u00f8rsel av uudnyttet \u00e5rlig ferie; konsultere HR / juridisk. N\u00e5r den er aktivert, kan ubrugte \u00e5rlige dager for \u00e5ret f\u00f8jes til n\u00e6ste \u00e5rs fremf\u00f8rsels\u00e5pneing, med forbehold for det maksimale overf\u00f8rselsloft ovenfor.",
