    "Opening balance hours must be a number between -9999 and 9999." : "\u00c5pneingssaldotimer skal v\u00e6re et tal mellem -9999 og 9999.",
    "Opening balance of carryover days for the selected calendar year (Resturlaub), e.g. from HR or migration. This is not the annual vacation entitlement from the working time model. The last day carryover can be used is set globally in Admin settings." : "\u00c5pneingssaldo for overf\u00f8rselsdage for det valgte kalender\u00e5r (Resturlaub), f.eks. fra HR eller migration. Dette er ikke den \u00e5rlige ferieret fra arbeidstidsmodelllen. Den sidste dag, overf\u00f8rsel kan bruges, settles globalt i administratorinnstillinger.",
    "Opening balance year must be a four-digit year (e.g. 2026)." : "\u00c5pneingsbalance\u00e5ret skal v\u00e6re et firecifret \u00e5r (f.eks. 2026).",
