    "Optional reason or notes for your absence request" : "Valgfri begrunnelse eller merknader til din frav\u00e6rsforesp\u00f8rsel",
    "Optional: Add notes or details about this work period (e.g., project work, meetings, tasks)" : "Valgfrittt: Legg til notater eller detaljer om denne arbejdsperiode (f.eks. projektarbejde, m\u00f8der, opgaver)",
    "Optional: Record your break times. Breaks of at least 15 minutes count toward legal requirements (ArbZG \u00a74)." : "Valgfrittt: Registrer dine pausetider. Pauser p\u00e5 mindst 15 minutter t\u00e6ller med i lovkrav (ArbZG \u00a74).",
    "Optional: Record your break times. Breaks of at least 15 minutes count toward legal requirements (ArbZG \u00a74). You can add multiple breaks." : "Valgfrittt: Registrer dine pausetider. Pauser p\u00e5 mindst 15 minutter t\u00e6ller med i lovkrav (ArbZG \u00a74). Du kan legg tile flere pauser.",
    "Optional: Record your break times. German law requires breaks for work over 6 hours: 30 minutes for 6-9 hours, 45 minutes for 9+ hours. Shorter shifts have no break requirements. Automatic breaks are added when needed for compliance. You can add additional manual breaks." : "Valgfrittt: Registrer dine pausetider. Tysk lov krever pauser for arbejde over 6 timer: 30 minutter for 6-9 timer, 45 minutter for 9+ timer. Kortere vagter har ingen pausekrav. Automatiske pauser legg tiles, n\u00e5r det er n\u00f8dvendigt for etterlevelse. Du kan legg tile ytterligere manuelle pauser.",
