    "Upper bound: counts users without an L1/L2/L3 override at all. Some users may still be served by a higher layer." : "\u00d8vre gr\u00e6nse: t\u00e6ller brukere uden en L1/L2/L3-tilsides\u00e6ttelse overhovedet. Noen brukere kan fortsatt betjenes av et h\u00f8jere lag.",
    "Upper limit of daily working time in hours. German labor law (ArbZG) allows 8 hours normally, up to 10 in special cases." : "\u00d8vre gr\u00e6nse for daglig arbeidstid i timer. Tysk arbeidslovgivning (ArbZG) tillader normalt 8 timer, op til 10 i s\u00e6rlige tilf\u00e6lde.",
    "Use \"Start Break\" and \"End Break\" to record your breaks. The system will remind you if you forget." : "Brug \"Start pause\" og \"Afslut pause\" til at optage dine pauser. Systemet vil minde deg om, hvis du glemmer det.",
    "Use 0\u2013366 in steps of 0.5 (for example 25 or 25.5)." : "Brug 0\u2013366 i trin p\u00e5 0,5 (for eksempel 25 eller 25,5).",
    "Use ArbeitszeitCheck teams for approvals" : "Brug ArbeitszeitCheck-team til godkjennelser",
