    "What information do you want in the report?" : "Hvilke oplysninger \u00f8nsker du i rapporten?",
    "What kind of report do you need?" : "Hvilken slags rapport har du brug for?",
    "What time did you finish working?" : "Hvad tid var du f\u00e6rdig med at arbejde?",
    "What time did you finish working? (24-hour format, e.g. 17:00 for 5 PM. For night shifts, enter the next day's time)" : "Hvad tid var du f\u00e6rdig med at arbejde? (24-timers format, f.eks. 17:00 til 17:00. Skriv inn n\u00e6ste dags tid for nattevagter)",
    "What time did you finish working? (24-hour format, e.g., 17:00 for 5 PM. For night shifts, enter the next day's time)" : "Hvad tid var du f\u00e6rdig med at arbejde? (24-timers format, f.eks. 17:00 til 17:00. For nattevagter skal du indtaste n\u00e6ste dags tid)",
    "What time did you start working?" : "Hvorn\u00e5r begyndte du at arbejde?",
    "What time did you start working? (24-hour format, e.g. 09:00 for 9 AM or 17:30 for 5:30 PM)" : "Hvorn\u00e5r begyndte du at arbejde? (24-timers format, f.eks. 09:00 for 9:00 eller 17:30 for 17:30)",
    "What time did you start working? (24-hour format, e.g., 09:00 for 9 AM or 17:30 for 5:30 PM)" : "Hvorn\u00e5r begyndte du at arbejde? (24-timers format, f.eks. 09:00 for 9:00 eller 17:30 for 17:30)",
    "What was changed" : "Hvad ble endret",
    "What-if (optional)" : "Hvad hvis (valgfrittt)",
    "What-if mode: hypothetical team membership applied \u2014" : "Hvad hvis-tilstand: hypotetisk teammedlemskab anvendt \u2014",
    "When ProjectCheck is enabled, you can optionally link billing hours on a project the employee is allowed to use." : "N\u00e5r ProjectCheck er aktivert, kan du valgfrittt sammenk\u00e6de faktureringstimer p\u00e5 et projekt, medarbeideren kan bruke.",
    "When a colleague requests an absence and selects you as their substitute, you will see the request here." : "N\u00e5r en kollega anmoder om frav\u00e6r og velger deg som sin stedfortreder, vil du se foresp\u00f8rselen her.",
    "When a substitute is selected, emails can be sent at each step of the approval process." : "N\u00e5r en stedfortredet er valgt, kan e-mails sendes p\u00e5 hvert trin i godkjennelsesprocessen.",
    "When an absence is approved, the employee can receive an email with an iCalendar (.ics) attachment so they can add the absence to their calendar." : "N\u00e5r et frav\u00e6r er godkjent, kan medarbeideren modtage en e-mail med en iCalendar (.ics) knytt tilet fil, s\u00e5 de kan legg tile frav\u00e6ret til deres kalender.",
    "When did this break end?" : "Hvorn\u00e5r sluttede denne pause?",
    "When did this break start?" : "Hvorn\u00e5r startede denne pause?",
    "When did you finish working?" : "Hvorn\u00e5r ble du f\u00e6rdig med at arbejde?",
    "When did you start working?" : "Hvorn\u00e5r begyndte du at arbejde?",
    "When does your absence end?" : "Hvorn\u00e5r slutter ditt frav\u00e6r?",
    "When does your absence start?" : "Hvorn\u00e5r starter ditt frav\u00e6r?",
    "When employees take breaks, they must write a short reason. This helps ensure breaks are used correctly and comply with labor law." : "N\u00e5r medarbeidere holder pauser, skal de skrive en kort begrundelse. Dette er med til at sikre, at pauser bruges korrekt og overholder arbeidslovgivningen.",
    "When enabled, a daily task may copy unused carryover (and optionally unused annual days, see below) into the next calendar year\u2019s opening balance after the carryover deadline, unless a balance already exists for that year. Use the occ command for manual runs." : "N\u00e5r den er aktivert, kan en daglig opgave kopiere ubrugt overf\u00f8rsel (og eventuelt ubrugte \u00e5rlige dager, se nedenfor) til det n\u00e6ste kalender\u00e5rs \u00e5pneingssaldo etter overf\u00f8rselsfristen, medmindre der allerede eksisterer en saldo for det p\u00e5g\u00e6ldende \u00e5r. Brug kommandoen occ til manuelle k\u00f8rsler.",
    "When enabled, breaks required by German law are automatically added. Disable to manage breaks manually." : "N\u00e5r den er aktivert, legg tiles pauser, der kreves av tysk lov, automatisk. Deaktiver for at administrere pauser manuelt.",
    "When enabled, employees can finalize a calendar month to create a tamper-evident snapshot (hash) and PDF. Finalized months stay locked even if this option is turned off later. Reopening a month is limited to administrators." : "N\u00e5r det er aktivert, kan medarbeiderne afslutte en kalenderm\u00e5ned for at opprettte et manipulationssikkert snapshot (hash) og PDF. Afsluttede m\u00e5neder forblir l\u00e5st, selv om denne mulighed sl\u00e5s fra senere. Gen\u00e5pneing en m\u00e5ned er begr\u00e6nset til administratorer.",
    "When enabled, employees cannot seal a month while hours above the bank cap are still unpaid for that month." : "N\u00e5r det er aktivert, kan medarbeidere ikke forsegle en m\u00e5ned, mens timer over bankgr\u00e6nsen fortsatt er ul\u00f8nnete for den m\u00e5ned.",
    "When enabled, entries that run across midnight (for example 22:00\u201306:00) are shown as two lines in the export (before and after 00:00). This is only a visual/export split \u2013 all internal working time and ArbZG compliance checks continue to use the original, unsplit entry." : "N\u00e5r det er aktivert, vises poster, der l\u00f8ber over midnat (for eksempel 22:00\u201306:00), som to linjer i eksporten (f\u00f8r og etter 00:00). Dette er kun en visuel/eksportopdeling \u2013 al intern arbeidstid og ArbZG-overensstemmelseskontrol forts\u00e6tter med at bruke den originale, uopdelte post.",
    "When enabled, missing statutory holidays are added when the calendar is viewed. Disable if you want deleted holidays to stay removed." : "N\u00e5r den er aktivert, legg tiles manglende lovp\u00e5lagte helligdager, n\u00e5r kalenderen vises. Deaktiver, hvis du \u00f8nsker, at slettede helligdager forblir fjernet.",
    "When enabled, selected workflow events send email updates to the configured HR recipients." : "N\u00e5r det er aktivert, sender udvalgte workflowh\u00e6ndelser e-mailoppdateringer til de konfigurerede HR-mottakere.",
    "When enabled, transitions to yellow or red levels can trigger in-app and email notifications." : "N\u00e5r det er aktivert, kan overgange til gule eller r\u00f8de niveauer udl\u00f8se meddelelser i appen og e-mail.",
    "When on: managers are taken from the ArbeitszeitCheck teams you define below. When off: managers are determined from shared Nextcloud groups (default behaviour)." : "N\u00e5r t\u00e6ndt: ledere tages fra de ArbeitszeitCheck-team, du definerer nedenfor. N\u00e5r deaktivert: ledere bestemmes ud fra delte Nextcloud-grupper (standardadf\u00e6rd).",
    "When someone works too many hours or doesn't take required breaks, the system will send a notification to managers and the employee." : "N\u00e5r noen jobber for mange timer eller ikke holder de n\u00f8dvendige pauser, sender systemet en meddelelse til ledere og medarbeideren.",
    "When this rule applies" : "N\u00e5r denne regel g\u00e6lder",
    "When you finished. Night shifts: use the next calendar day if end is after midnight." : "N\u00e5r du er f\u00e6rdig. Nattevagter: Brug den n\u00e6ste kalenderdag, hvis slutningen er etter midnat.",
    "When you started (e.g. 09:00)." : "Da du startede (f.eks. 09:00).",
